    "RESULTS AND ANALYSIS 6.1 Main ResultsThe main results are shown in Table 1.",
    "It can be observed that:(1) Our proposed MetaRAG consistently surpasses all baseline methods across two datasets.",
    "When compared to Reflexion, which also integrates a self-critic mechanism in its reasoning process, MetaRAG demonstrates a substantial improvement on all metrics.",
    "This suggests that using a metacognitive strategy is more beneficial than merely relying on self-criticism.",
    "By leveraging metacognitive knowledge and regulation, our method aligns better with human thought."
  ]
